Written using Ruby 2.1.5p273

Run '$ gem install bundler'
Run '$ gem install rspec'
Run '$ gem install pry'

Launch Sinatra app with '$ ruby app.rb'

Go to https://local:host4567/

GPL v2 Copyright 2015 Crystal Contreras-Grossman

Known bugs:

Phone number input cannot take specific phone number types,
(ie: cell, work, home) at this point in time.
The radios for the phone number options are installed, however,
they are unresponsive when it comes to applying
the option to the additional phone number.
